parameters: \nw[Taro]Should I talk to Kuno and Nonna?

\nw[Taro]It's a spacious room, isn't it? It seems like we
can use the other two rooms as well, so sleeping
shouldn't be a problem.

\nw[Taro]For now, shall we try talking about what everyone
is doing?
$gameVariables._data[$gameVariables.value(111)][26] = 0//エロステ表示、１で表示他で非表示

\nw[Thorz]Oh boy, I'd like to take a carriage for such a
long journey.

\nw[Dalton]Even though you're young, you're so sloppy. As a
magician, you should also train your body.

\nw[Huma]This is a big bed. With this, you can have fun
with quite a number of people.
\nw[Rodrigo]Uka... You might have more experience than me.

\nw[Nonna]Taro, I have something to talk about. Do you have
some time?

\nw[Nonna]I was talking to Kuno, and it seems like you've
been troubled lately, haven't you?

\nw[Nonna]There may be things that you can't say. But if you
tell us, we'll support you. Both me and Kuno.

\nw[Taro]I have one thing to discuss right away. It seems
like I've upset Louis and he's started to dislike
me... Even when I try to talk to him, he
completely ignores me except for work-related
matters.
\nw[Taro]Ah, I see. So, how can I make him like me again...
\nw[Nonna]Do you have any idea what might be causing it?

\nw[Taro](There's no way I can tell them that I was seen
walking around with an erection...!)
\nw[Taro]Well, it's not something I can easily say...

\nw[Nonna]It's difficult to give proper advice if we don't
know the cause...

\nw[Nonna]If you know the cause, it's important to reflect
on that and then apologize properly.

\nw[Taro]Ah, I tried that, but even if I apologize, I'm
being ignored.

\nw[Nonna]Is that so... In that case, I think it's best to
continue. You have to show sincerity and make the
other person understand.

\nw[Kuno]How about apologizing by giving her something she
likes? Some people believe that sincerity can be
expressed through gifts.

\nw[Taro]I see, something she likes... Speaking of what
Louis likes...

\nw[Taro]...I remember she said her hobby is cosplay. In
that case...what should I do?

\nw[Kuno]Cosplay, huh... I don't really understand it, but
it's about wearing unique clothes, right?

\nw[Taro]I see... Oh, come to think of it, I remember
saying that I wanted to get along with a beautiful
woman who enjoys cosplay.
\nw[Kuno]I see... Wait, are you into that kind of thing!?

\nw[Taro]No, she said she's not interested in anything
sexual. It seems like she just wants to cosplay.

\nw[Kuno]I don't really know how to describe that person.
She's generally sarcastic and doesn't talk about
herself.

\nw[Kuno]I hear she's capable at work, but I can't really
tell from my perspective...

\nw[Taro]Yeah, I don't really understand her... I don't
think she's the type to get angry or upset and
show those kinds of emotions...

\nw[Kuno]Yeah... If that's the case, I'm even more unsure
about what to do...

\nw[Taro]Well, if I apologize again when I get home... but
if she still ignores me... I wonder what I should
do.

\nw[Nonna]If it continues for a long time, we'll have no
choice but to forcefully create an opportunity to
talk. At that time, let's ask Prae to create a
space for discussion.
\nw[Taro]I see... Yeah, got it. I'll do that.

\nw[Nonna]Hehehe, if I could be of help, then thank
goodness.

\nw[Taro]Both of you, feel free to come to me with any
concerns. If you're in trouble, I want to be able
to help.

\nw[Kuno]It's not a consultation, but there's something I
want to say...

\nw[Nonna]Yes, I'll be waiting, so please do it as soon as
possible.
